{"type": "article", "id": 32612, "title": "Lululemon 越来越爱卖男装，以及，COS 的新作很好看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-26T02:27:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 33156, "name": "彩虹高光"}, {"id": 33159, "name": "OMbra"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 3530, "name": "Forever 21"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 8367, "name": "lululemon"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 23652, "name": "Becca"}, {"id": 33157, "name": "UEG"}, {"id": 33160, "name": "OMsignal"}, {"id": 33158, "name": "Agnes Martin"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160926095658I4Y2pm1BrWtTKj9u.jpg", "contents": "<h3>&nbsp;一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/lululemon-looks-to-get-40-of-sales-from-men-as-chain-expands\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Lululemon 的男性消费者将超 40%</b></a> | 现阶段，Lululemon 的消费者有近 80% 都是女性。但是，据它的 CEO Laurent Potdevin 所称，随着 Lululemon 的海外扩张，消费者对于它原本的女性瑜伽品牌的认知不断减弱，它的男性消费者将占 40%。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSFWN1BY0R6?feedType=RSS\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Moncler 大股东 Eurazeo 出售 6% 股权</b></a> | 意大利 Moncler 集团的大股东，法国投资公司 Eurazeo 将所持有的 Moncler 1500 万股售出，这次出售的股份约占 Moncler 集团的 6% 股权，价值约为 2.3 亿欧元。Eurazeo 获利约 1.9 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/estee-lauder-said-to-be-eyeing-becca-cosmetics-10562535/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛或将加入 Becca 的收购战中</b></a> | 有消息称，美国彩妆品牌 Becca 将被出售给两家私人股权公司，售价为 2 亿美元，不过该交易未达成。今年七月，雅诗兰黛的竞争对手欧莱雅集团斥资 12 亿美元收购 IT Cosmetics，此举或将刺激雅诗兰黛加入对 Becca 的收购中。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://betakit.com/omsignal-announces-13-million-in-funding-alongside-launch-of-smart-bra/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>加拿大女性智能运动文胸初创公司 OMsignal 获得 1000 万美元融资</b></a> | OMsignal 是一家总部位于蒙特利尔的健身跟踪设备公司，耗时两年研发出了女性智能运动文胸 OMbra，该文胸已于 9 月 19 日发售，入门款售价为 79 美元。本次融资由 Relay Ventures 领投。 &nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>COS 推出了以已故的美国画家 Agnes Martin 的作品为灵感的<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/cos-agnes-martin-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">胶囊系列</a>，该系列中使用了 Martin 作品中经典的几何结构，创造出了一系列有着独特图案的极简单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609260951018UqRSVfY3BphAM2l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095101FT0Wr64ZEkxOHu9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095101JjQBqDfncAua9wEd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095101iR0ZKVhONxP3ytLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609260951025M6VSx8lgdIBOUaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095102WPkDVutUnziG9gK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Forever 21 也推出了在 Instagram 上大热的<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/forever-21-rainbow-highlighterr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">彩虹高光</a>，网店限定，只售 6 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095118SjD8mwRiJHQ5hscW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609260951183ro2pNmhajKxLYls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">PUMA 与波兰品牌 UEG 推出全新联名系列。该系列以<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/puma-ueg-2016-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Gravity Resistance </a>为主题，发布了一系列包括风衣外套、连身洋装、短袖上衣、短裤等多款单品。该系列以宇航员服装为样式，抗重力的前卫设计理念结合了弹性材质，展现一种未来科技感。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095143bz8OCnrFPGvygIpw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609260951434G0rcv6wKIWJbOfM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095143ynG78OPL0mudQCRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095159ANO1ykZ6C4R8rxmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095159e1oU43Jcu8NBtXpK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095200kJAO5ZSPIlM0naV6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095159hPQwzCiOuBZVkeMf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095209VqizSmosL29nT4vt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/naked-x-vans-designed-the-prettiest-pastel-pack-petal-pink-and-hint-of-mint/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Naked 与 Vans 推出联名款</a>，这款的鞋身以皮革编织而成，有薄荷绿和梦幻粉两种颜色，鞋带和鞋身均使用了同款颜色，全球限量 100 双。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095044UfHDGMAuXKgI14Cl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095037v2ALMO5kQDEgJ7pr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095025sDrnZ6uOw5RT2CYe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/kith-2016-fall-first-delivery\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH 发布 2016 秋季新作 lookbook</a>，该系列新品与针织面料专家 Calux 合作，开发了保暖性高的运动裤、连帽衫、长袖 T-shirt 等多款单品，现已于美国东部时间 9 月 24 日登陆 KITH 指定门店。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095245b78uGZRkjfJi1S56.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095255mpMrKBOh2dbnjFaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095256G2gYwiSjVRuc9nPt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609260952568m4Ly9QM1qRui5Ng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095256gAMxRFk67p5v2UzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095257aj0dk526A4E8PgRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095257bIwBvtnCuOyTsqid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095305NQo3jvGnfw0XW4ST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095305HPUYvs62Qd4yg1Za.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160926095305Zzgu2hYB51T9cwMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}